1. Entities

Our Real Estate Business Database will contain 11 tables.

No	Entity (Table)	Description
1	PropertyOwner	Stores property owner information
2	Agent	Stores employee information
3	Customer	Stores customer information
4	PropertyType	Types of properties
5	Property	Stores all property details
6	Visit	Records customer property visits
7	Sale	Records sold properties
8	Rental	Records rented properties
9	Payment	Records customer payments
10	Holiday	Stores public holidays (used by triggers)
11	AuditLog	Stores user activity logs
